reviewText: Originally 'beyond the Limits', 2 part borefest stretched over 2 hours... gory german trash-movie that has nothing to do with Zombies... don't waste your time or money.
This is actually "Beyond The Limits" from 2003, not a new Ittenbach film. This has nothing to do with zombies.

This was more two shorts that are linked by a "storyteller" of sorts. Lots of gore but nothing special otherwise. I was very disappointed and if you think this is a zombie movie you will surprised to know that there was not a single one in the movie.
